sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Student Client
    participant ALB as ALB<br/>(HTTP :80)
    participant API as FastAPI Service<br/>(ECS Fargate x2)
    participant DDB as DynamoDB<br/>(campus-print-jobs)
    participant S3 as S3 Bucket<br/>(campus-print-docs)
    participant SQS as SQS Queue<br/>(per-printer)
    participant W as Printer Worker<br/>(ECS Fargate x3)

    rect rgb(219, 234, 254)
        Note over C,S3: Upload Flow (POST /jobs)
        C->>+ALB: POST /jobs (multipart: file + userId)
        ALB->>+API: Forward request
        API->>API: Generate UUID jobId<br/>Sanitize filename
        API->>+S3: PutObject (uploads/{jobId}/{fileName})
        S3-->>-API: 200 OK
        API->>+DDB: PutItem (status=HELD, version=1, TTL=24h)
        DDB-->>-API: 200 OK
        API-->>-ALB: 201 {jobId, status: HELD}
        ALB-->>-C: 201 Created
    end

    rect rgb(237, 220, 255)
        Note over C,SQS: Release Flow (POST /jobs/{id}/release)
        C->>+ALB: POST /jobs/{id}/release {printerName}
        ALB->>+API: Forward request
        API->>+DDB: UpdateItem<br/>SET status=RELEASED, printerName<br/>CONDITION status=HELD
        DDB-->>-API: 200 OK (version=2)
        API->>+SQS: SendMessage ({jobId, s3Key, printerName})
        SQS-->>-API: 200 OK
        API-->>-ALB: 200 {status: RELEASED}
        ALB-->>-C: 200 OK

        Note over API,SQS: On SQS failure: compensating write<br/>RELEASED -> HELD (rollback)
    end

    rect rgb(209, 250, 229)
        Note over SQS,DDB: Processing Flow (Worker)
        loop Long Poll (20s wait)
            W->>+SQS: ReceiveMessage (MaxMessages=1)
            SQS-->>-W: Message {jobId, s3Key}
        end
        W->>+DDB: UpdateItem<br/>SET status=PROCESSING<br/>CONDITION status=RELEASED
        DDB-->>-W: 200 OK (version=3)
        W->>+S3: GetObject (fetch document)
        S3-->>-W: Document bytes
        W->>W: Simulate printing<br/>(process document)
        W->>+DDB: UpdateItem<br/>SET status=DONE<br/>CONDITION status=PROCESSING
        DDB-->>-W: 200 OK (version=4)
        W->>SQS: DeleteMessage
    end

    rect rgb(254, 226, 226)
        Note over SQS,DDB: Fault Recovery (crash mid-processing)
        Note right of W: Worker crashes after PROCESSING<br/>ECS replaces task (~60s)<br/>SQS visibility timeout expires
        SQS->>+W: Redeliver message (receiveCount > 1)
        W->>+DDB: GetItem (check current status)
        DDB-->>-W: status=PROCESSING, receiveCount>1
        W->>W: Re-process (idempotent)
        W->>+DDB: UpdateItem SET status=DONE
        DDB-->>-W: 200 OK
        W->>-SQS: DeleteMessage
    end
